title: The Scientists' 101 Top Free Agents
itunes:title: The Scientists' 101 Top Free Agents
description:
A stadium filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler go through Chris and Gregg's Top 101 Free Agents list. The heroes argue about where they think some of these big names are listed and where they think they'll go. Plus, an exclusive JAWS recap.
